h the \"to\" parameter.\";'),('ru','messages:rest-param-desc-pagehistory-count-title','s:47:\"ru:Заголовок вики-страницы\";'),('ru','messages:rest-param-desc-pagehistory-count-to','s:114:\"en:Restricts the count to between two revisions, specified by revision ID. Must be used with the \"from\" parameter.\";'),('ru','messages:rest-param-desc-pagehistory-count-type','s:66:\"en:Type of count (anonymous, bot, editors, edits, minor, reverted)\";'),('ru','messages:rest-param-desc-pagehistory-filter','s:117:\"en:Use a filter to return only revisions tagged as (reverted, anonymous, bot, minor). Accepts one filter per request.\";'),('ru','messages:rest-param-desc-pagehistory-newer-than','s:89:\"en:Accepts a revision ID. Returns the next 20 revisions newer than the given revision ID.\";'),('ru','messages:rest-param-desc-pagehistory-older-than','s:89:\"en:Accepts a revision ID. Returns the next 20 revisions older than the given revision ID.\";'),('ru','messages:rest-param-desc-pagehistory-title','s:47:\"ru:Заголовок вики-страницы\";'),('ru','messages:rest-param-desc-revision-id','s:42:\"ru:Идентификатор правки\";'),('ru','messages:rest-param-desc-search-limit','s:77:\"en:Maximum number of search results to return, between 1 and 100. Default: 50\";'),('ru','messages:rest-param-desc-search-q','s:30:\"ru:Условия поиска\";'),('ru','messages:rest-param-desc-source','s:69:\"en:Page content in the format specified by the content_model property\";'),('ru','messages:rest-param-desc-transform-format','s:19:\"en:Transform format\";'),('ru','messages:rest-param-desc-transform-from','s:17:\"en:Transform from\";'),('ru','messages:rest-param-desc-transform-revision','s:21:\"en:Transform revision\";'),('ru','messages:rest-param-desc-transform-title','s:18:\"en:Transform title\";'),('ru','messages:rest-param-desc-update-latest','s:198:\"ru:Информация о новейшей версии страницы. Вы можете получить эту информацию из источника источника страницы.\";'),('ru','messages:rest-param-desc-update-source